### Create Employee
POST http://localhost:4000/employee-api
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John ",
    "email": "john.doe@example.com",
    "mobile": "1234567890",
    "designation": "Software Engineer",
    "companyName": "Tech Corp"
}

### Get All Employees
GET http://localhost:4000/employee-api

### Edit Employee (Update ID first)
PUT http://localhost:4000/employee-api/<ID_HERE>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "John Updated",
    "designation": "Senior Software Engineer"
}

### Delete Employee (Update ID first)
DELETE http://localhost:4000/employee-api/<ID_HERE>
